- Rats.
- Oh.

42:58.659 --> 43:00.535
- Um! "They fought the dogs
and killed the cats,

43:00.661 --> 43:02.537
"and bit the babies in the cradles,

43:02.663 --> 43:05.456
"and ate the cheeses
